headline: Heritage Celebrates 60 Years as North America’s Longest-Standing Military Coater
summary: AKRON, Ohio, July 20, 2025--Heritage marks 60 yrs as North America's oldest military coater, pioneering CARC since 1965 with all OEMs. Targets $5M sales via automation.
